 ('198','510','Lament of the Supernaturalist','walrrot.png','3','60','120','Dr. Emmerset Wilsongraft dedicated his life to the discovery of new species.  The more bizarre the species, the happier he was to publicize it.  As such, he came to be something of a world-renowned go-to guy for anyone with a weird creature problem.  Most such claims were shallow attempts at leeching fame, but several were legit.  When Dr. Wilsongraft met his first Deep One, he never looked back to mere variants on a theme of normalcy and sound sleep.  Now the good doctor has gone missing, and you and your companions have been summoned by his daughter Lucrecia, the wealthy-to-be heiress to his estate, to get to the bottom of his disappearance...','','','1','','0','0','20 23'),
